      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows substantial wear, including heavy rusting on the rocker panels, large dents, and peeling clear coat across several body panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock and several fluid leaks that need immediate repair. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be a suitable project car or a candidate for parts, as it is not currently recommended for daily commuting without major repairs.",
