      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained to the highest standards with an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance and presentation that mirror its initial delivery. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand perfection.",
