    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. I've babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel. I'm sad to let it go, but I'm excited for it to find a great new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
