    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous gloss that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin still retains that new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records available. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage remains pristine. This isn't just a used car; it is an investment-grade specimen perfect for a collector or an enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
